        ))
      }

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<style>
.price-image{
  display:block;

  overflow:hidden;

  margin-bottom:18px;

  border-radius:22px;

  border:1px solid var(--border);

  background:var(--card);
}

.price-image img{
  width:100%;
  height:auto;

  display:block;

  transition:transform .35s ease;
}

.price-card:hover .price-image img{
  transform:scale(1.03);
}
</style>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">

      <h2 class="section-title">
        FAQ
      </h2>

      <p class="section-desc">
        Pertanyaan umum tentang AI Mr Ferdy.
      </p>

      <div class="faq-item">

        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>
            Apa itu AI Mr Ferdy?
          </span>

          <div class="faq-icon"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>
            AI Mr Ferdy adalah platform digital yang fokus pada
            AI systems, SEO technology, automation dan website modern.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">

        <div class="faq-question">
          <span>
            Apakah website mobile friendly?
          </span>

          <div class="faq-icon"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>
            Ya, seluruh platform dibangun mobile first dan optimized
